    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">妾</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>FEMALE MATE who is NOT a WIFE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>Fēi 妃 (ant. wáng 王 "king") refers to a royal concubine.</p>
        </div>
<div type="huang-jingui">
<p>HUANG JINGUI 2006</p>
<p>HUMAN AFFAIRS 小妻。</p>
<p>妾，總稱。</p>
<p>媵，媵婚制下特指隨嫁的侄女（姪）、妹妹（娣）；漢以後變為妾，常與 “ 妾 ” 、 “ 婢 ” 連用。</p>
<p>娣，媵婚制後，泛指相當妾的陪嫁女子，常指幼妾。</p>
<p>姬，豪門大戶有色藝或得寵的妾。</p>
<p>嬙、嬪、御，宮中女官，同為天子妾，地位由高到低。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
